title: 47 Easy-to-Do Classic Science Experiments (2012).epub Gooner
description:
47 Easy-to-Do Classic Science Experiments (2012).epub Gooner

Publisher: Dover Publications (July 31, 2012)
Publication Date: July 31, 2012
Language: English
ASIN: B00A3ZDW98

This highly motivating book for grade-school students will introduce them to many of the world's most popular scientific experiments. Over 40 simple but enjoyable experiments, performed with common household items, teach youngsters principles of light, elasticity, perspective, gravity, air pressure, optics, more. Includes nearly 70 illustrations
